# @afenda/docs — Fumadocs documentation site
#
# Runtime env (optional):
#   DOCS_GITHUB_TOKEN          — GitHub REST token for last-modified timestamps during
#                                production/preview builds (contents:read on afenda-Xerp).
#                                Skipped in local dev (`pnpm --filter @afenda/docs dev`).
#   DOCS_GITHUB_API_BASE_URL   — Optional GitHub Enterprise API root (default: https://api.github.com)
#   OPENROUTER_API_KEY         — OpenRouter API key for Ask AI (`/api/chat`). Required for AI chat.
#   OPENROUTER_MODEL           — Optional model id (default: anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet).
#   DOCS_GITHUB_APP_ID         — GitHub App id for docs feedback → Discussions (optional).
#   DOCS_GITHUB_APP_PRIVATE_KEY — GitHub App PEM private key (optional; use \n for newlines).
#
# Sync from repo root via `pnpm env:console refresh` → apps/docs/.env.local
# Do NOT copy ERP auth/database secrets into this project.
#
# Local dev:
#   pnpm --filter @afenda/docs dev    # http://localhost:3001
#
# Vercel docs project: separate project with Root Directory = apps/docs.
# Set DOCS_GITHUB_TOKEN on production + preview for last-modified footer.
